data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! Nestled on the north side of Hanford in a well established neighborhood, this is an enchanting residence filled with modern comforts. As you step through the front door, you're greeted by a warm and inviting ambiance. As you walk through the kitchen  you can truly admire the open feeling and the ample space to enjoy all the family gatherings.  Take a look at the  magnificent fireplace that serves as the heart of the living room.
The spacious living area is bathed in natural light, creating a cozy atmosphere to unwind and relax. 
But the allure doesn't end there. Step outside onto the expansive porch, and you'll be captivated by  the outdoor space. Along with so many other features, don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours.
This home wont last long, make your appointment today!
